1. *On* zove svog druga da dođe van. (He is calling his friend to come outside.)
2. *Zovemo* ga da nam pomogne. (We are calling him to help us.)
3. *Zvala* ga je da joj pomogne. (She was calling him to help her.)
4. *Zvao* sam ga da mi kaže da li je došao. (I called him to tell me if he had come.)
5. *Zvao* je da ode kod njega. (He was calling her to go to him.)